<p rend="chapter">Juhotyā’dayo <pb ed="V" n="0.0023" /> sadvibhāvaluttavikaraṇā.</p>

<p rend="hangnum" n="100"><hi rend="paranum">100</hi><hi rend="dot">.</hi></p>

<p rend="gatha1"> Hū dāne’(pi ca) ādāne havyadāne (ca vattate,)</p>

<p rend="gathalast">Hā cāge kamu yātrāyaṃ dā dāne dhā (ca) dhāraṇe;</p>

<p rend="centre">Avikaraṇabhūvādayo samattā.</p>
